{
  "style": "",
  "texts": [
    "Peters et al.",
    "report one model built to predict the number of internal details in individual narratives.",
    "RMSE for this model was approximately.75 for episodic future thinking narratives and.85 for autobiographical memory narratives.",
    "No model was reported that predicted semantic details in individual narratives.",
    "To contextualize these results, a simple model that predicts the mean number of internal or semantic details for every narrative in this dataset would result in RMSE = 1, while a model with perfect predictions would result in RMSE = 0."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}